{
  "text": "Since echinocandins show a concentration-dependent activity in experimental models of infections due to Candida species other than C. guilliermondii and C. parapsilosis [CITATION_1] , further studies employing additional doses are needed to clarify this issue in these two species as well.",
  "correct_citation": {
